M|prioritization-advisor|- [Rationale 2]
M|prioritization-advisor|- [Rationale 3]
M|prioritization-advisor|**When to use it:**
M|prioritization-advisor|- [ctx where this framework excels]
M|prioritization-advisor|**When NOT to use it:**
M|prioritization-advisor|- [Limitations or contexts where it fails]
